'''達利戰役'''（{{lang-en|Battle of Dhale}}）是從2015年3月24日開始的軍事衝突，屬於[[也门内战_(2014年至今)|也门内战 (2014年至今)]]的一部分。[[胡塞武裝組織|胡塞武裝組織]]和效忠於前總統[[阿里·阿卜杜拉·薩利赫|阿里·阿卜杜拉·薩利赫]]的軍隊聯手，與效忠於國際公認的總統[[阿卜杜拉布·曼蘇爾·哈迪|阿卜杜拉布·曼蘇爾·哈迪]]的軍隊為了爭奪{{link-en|達利 (葉門)|Ad Dali'|達利}}而發生衝突。

== 戰役 ==
3月24日，胡塞武裝組織攻下達利的行政建築，並在猛烈砲火下逐步推進。發生於第33裝甲旅軍營的戰鬥直到下午才結束，造成10名反哈迪份子死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.romandie.com/news/Les-forces-hostiles-au-president-resserrent-l039etau/577912.rom|title=Les forces hostiles au président resserrent l'étau sur Aden|agency=Romandie|date=2015-03-24|accessdate=2015-03-24|language=fr}}</ref>。隨後，親哈迪的部隊開始展開反攻，將胡塞份子擊退<ref>{{cite news|title=Hadi forces check Houthi push towards Yemen's Aden|agency=Reuters|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/24/us-yemen-security-idUSKBN0MK16O20150324|date=2015-03-24|accessdate=2015-03-25}}</ref>。

3月30日，經過將近一星期的戰鬥後，胡塞終於進入了達利城內<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.criticalthreats.org/gulf-aden-security-review/gulf-aden-security-review-march-30-2015#_edn4|title=Gulf of Aden Security Review - March 30, 2015 - Critical Threats|publisher=|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。據報導兩方各佔據達利城部分區域<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/airstrikes-shake-yemens-capital-shiite-rebels-push-south-30000813|title=Saudi-Led Forces Strike Yemen Rebels, Blockade Ports|author=ABC News|work=ABC News|accessdate=9 April 2015}}</ref>，但有當地的[[謝赫_(稱號)|謝赫]]表示胡塞已經控制了達利城，且零星的戰鬥仍持續發生，雙方都遭受「慘重的傷亡」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1872/news/5016/Fighting-spreads-into-five-southern-governorates.htm|title=Fighting spreads into five southern governorates|work=Yemen Times|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331103411/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1872/news/5016/Fighting-spreads-into-five-southern-governorates.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。也在此時，一名[[國際紅十字與紅新月運動|紅新月會]]的救護車司機因車輛被砲火擊中而喪生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.petra.gov.jo/Public_News/Nws_NewsDetails.aspx?Site_Id=1&lang=2&NewsID=190040&CatID=13&Type=Home&GType=1|title=Jordan News Agency (Petra) -WHO deplores deaths of health care workers in Yemen|publisher=|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150407222944/http://www.petra.gov.jo/Public_News/Nws_NewsDetails.aspx?Site_Id=1&lang=2&NewsID=190040&CatID=13&Type=Home&GType=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

3月31日，和哈迪合作的{{link-en|南方運動|Southern Movement}}成員與胡塞、親沙雷軍隊交戰。此外，反覆的空襲也成功擊中了胡塞聯軍軍營的彈藥庫。當天的戰鬥造成大約30名胡塞聯軍及9名南方運動份子陣亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/31/us-yemen-security-idUSKBN0MR0HE20150331|agency=Reuters|title=Heavy clashes on Saudi-Yemeni border; Hadi government pleads for troops|date=2015-03-31|accessdate=2015-03-31}}</ref>。

4月1日，親胡塞的第33裝甲旅據說被聯軍空襲重創後「瓦解」，該旅指揮官已經逃亡別處。胡塞也向北退卻<ref name="disintegrates">{{cite news|url=http://www.worldbulletin.net/todays-news/157273/pro-houthi-brigade-disintegrates-in-yemens-ad-dali|agency=World Bulletin|title=Pro-Houthi brigade disintegrates in Yemen's Ad Dali|date=2015-04-01|accessdate=2015-04-01}}</ref>。10名親哈迪軍隊於巷戰中陣亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/01/us-yemen-security-idUSKBN0MS4Y120150401|title=Yemen Houthi fighters backed by tanks reach central Aden|work=Reuters|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。隔天，達利城被哈迪軍隊所控制，但和胡塞份子的槍戰仍持續發生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2015/04/02/uk-yemen-security-idUKKBN0MP0LZ20150402|title=Yemen's Houthis seize central Aden district, presidential site|work=Reuters UK|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。

4月4日，胡塞攻下了該城的中央監獄，讓囚犯選擇加入胡塞組織或是繼續被監禁，造成三百人離開了監獄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2015/04/04/shiite-free-hundreds-of-prisoners-in-yemen-officials-say.html|title=Shiites free hundreds of prisoners in Yemen, officials say|date=4 April 2015|work=thestar.com|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。

4月5日，針對胡塞份子的空襲擊中了住宅區，使得5位平民喪生<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2015/04/05/4883402_senior-yemeni-sunni-leaders-abducted.html?rh=1 |title=Senior Yemeni Sunni leaders abducted by Shiite rebels |access-date=2015-05-16 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150407224847/http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2015/04/05/4883402_senior-yemeni-sunni-leaders-abducted.html?rh=1 |archive-date=2015-04-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。隔晚，19名胡塞份子和15名親哈迪軍隊在戰鬥中陣亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3027228/Dozens-dead-southern-Yemen-clashes.html|title=Yemen clashes kill more than 140 as aid delayed|work=Mail Online|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。

4月8日，聯軍向達利的胡塞份子發動更多的空襲行動<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/08/us-yemen-security-idUSKBN0MY1TL20150408|title=Yemen's Houthis battle in central Aden, first medical aid arrives|work=Reuters|accessdate=2015-04-09}}</ref>。

當地官員表示4月12日至4月13日期間，40名胡塞份子與三名親哈迪軍隊死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gulf-daily-news.com/NewsDetails.aspx?storyid=399966|title=Gulf Daily News » World News » Yemen unrest driven by Iran's hunger for power|publisher=|accessdate=26 April 2015}}</ref>，另外有三名孩童因家被砲彈擊中而喪生<ref name="vote">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3036647/Saudi-led-planes-hit-Yemen-rebels-gunfire-kills-five.html|title=UN Security council to vote on Yemen Huthi resolution|work=Mail Online|accessdate=2015-04-26}}</ref>。4月18日，逐漸增多的戰鬥和空襲造成31名胡塞份子及17名親哈迪軍隊陣亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3045497/Clashes-Yemen-rebels-president-allies-kill-21.html|title=Yemen rebel leader vows resistance against Saudi-led air war|work=Mail Online|accessdate=2015-04-26}}</ref>。

此外在4月22日和4月25日，根據親哈迪方的消息指出，至少20名親胡塞份子與8名當地武裝份子死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/23/us-yemen-security-idUSKBN0NC2LD20150423|agency=Reuters|title=Saudi-led coalition launches air strikes throughout Yemen: residents|date=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-04-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shanghaidaily.com/article/article_xinhua.aspx?id=278606|title=63 killed, dozens wounded in fighting, airstrikes in southern Yemen - Shanghai Daily|publisher=|accessdate=2015-04-26}}</ref>。

